      "title": "Recycling Machine",
      "pageid": 1696,
      "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div id=\"infoboxborder\">\n<table id=\"infoboxtable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxheader\">Recycling Machine</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding-bottom: 5px; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/File:Recycling_Machine.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Recycling Machine.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/2/26/Recycling_Machine.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"96\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxdetail\" style=\"text-align: center; font-style: italic; padding-right: 3px;\">Turns fishing trash into resources.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0;\">Information</td>\n</tr>\n\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Source</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><a href=\"/Crafting\" title=\"Crafting\">Crafting</a></td>\n\t</tr> \n\t<tr>\n\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Sell Price</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><i>Cannot be sold</i>\n\t\t</td>\n</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0;\">Crafting</td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Recipe Source</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120955\">.mw-parser-output .nametemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplate img,.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Fishing Skill Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e7/Fishing_Skill_Icon.png/24px-Fishing_Skill_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e7/Fishing_Skill_Icon.png/36px-Fishing_Skill_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e7/Fishing_Skill_Icon.png/48px-Fishing_Skill_Icon.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Fishing\" title=\"Fishing\">Fishing</a>&#160;(Level 4)</span></td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Ingredients</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Wood.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/df/Wood.png/24px-Wood.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/df/Wood.png/36px-Wood.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/df/Wood.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Wood\" title=\"Wood\">Wood</a>&#160;(25)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Stone.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d4/Stone.png/24px-Stone.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d4/Stone.png/36px-Stone.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/d4/Stone.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Stone\" title=\"Stone\">Stone</a>&#160;(25)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Iron Bar.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/6c/Iron_Bar.png/24px-Iron_Bar.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/6c/Iron_Bar.png/36px-Iron_Bar.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/6/6c/Iron_Bar.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Iron_Bar\" title=\"Iron Bar\">Iron Bar</a>&#160;(1)</span></td>\n\t</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p>The <b>Recycling Machine</b> is a <a href=\"/Crafting\" title=\"Crafting\">crafted</a> item that is used to turn <a href=\"/Trash\" title=\"Trash\">trash</a> (aside from the <a href=\"/Joja_Cola\" title=\"Joja Cola\">Joja Cola</a> and <a href=\"/Rotten_Plant\" title=\"Rotten Plant\">Rotten Plant</a>) into useful items. It takes <style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120974\">.mw-parser-output .durationtemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .durationtemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .durationtemplate img,.mw-parser-output .durationtemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"durationtemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Time Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/24px-Time_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/36px-Time_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/70/Time_Icon.png 2x\" /> 60m (1h)</span> to process items.<sup id=\"cite_ref-processtime_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-processtime-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The recipe is earned at <a href=\"/Skills#Fishing\" title=\"Skills\">Fishing level 4</a>.\n</p><p>One Recycling Machine is the reward for completing the <span style=\"display:inline; margin-right:0;\"><img alt=\"Bundle Blue.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Bundle_Blue.png/24px-Bundle_Blue.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Bundle_Blue.png/36px-Bundle_Blue.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/e4/Bundle_Blue.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Bundles#Field_Research_Bundle\" title=\"Bundles\">Field Research Bundle</a> on the <a href=\"/Bundles#Bulletin_Board\" title=\"Bundles\">Bulletin Board</a></span>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recycling\">Recycling</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Recycling_Machine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Recycling\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable roundedborder\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Image\n</th>\n<th>Name\n</th>\n<th>Description\n</th>\n<th>Produced from Recycling\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"3\"><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:Trash_(item).png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Trash (item).png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/7c/Trash_%28item%29.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></div></div>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/Trash_(item)\" title=\"Trash (item)\">Trash</a>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"3\">It's junk.\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Stone.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d4/Stone.png/24px-Stone.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d4/Stone.png/36px-Stone.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/d4/Stone.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Stone\" title=\"Stone\">Stone</a>&#160;(1-3)</span> &#160;<b>49%</b>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Coal.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a7/Coal.png/24px-Coal.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a7/Coal.png/36px-Coal.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/a7/Coal.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Coal\" title=\"Coal\">Coal</a>&#160;(1-3)</span> &#160;<b>30%</b>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"no-wrap\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Iron Ore.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/87/Iron_Ore.png/24px-Iron_Ore.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/87/Iron_Ore.png/36px-Iron_Ore.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/8/87/Iron_Ore.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Iron_Ore\" title=\"Iron Ore\">Iron Ore</a>&#160;(1-3)</span> &#160;<b>21%</b>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"2\"><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:Driftwood.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Driftwood.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/63/Driftwood.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></div></div>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Driftwood\" title=\"Driftwood\">Driftwood</a>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"2\">A piece of wood from the sea.\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Wood.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/df/Wood.png/24px-Wood.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/df/Wood.png/36px-Wood.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/df/Wood.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Wood\" title=\"Wood\">Wood</a>&#160;(1-3)</span> &#160;<b>75%</b>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Coal.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a7/Coal.png/24px-Coal.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a7/Coal.png/36px-Coal.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/a7/Coal.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Coal\" title=\"Coal\">Coal</a>&#160;(1-3)</span> &#160;<b>25%</b>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"2\"><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:Soggy_Newspaper.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Soggy Newspaper.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/c/c0/Soggy_Newspaper.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></div></div>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Soggy_Newspaper\" title=\"Soggy Newspaper\">Soggy Newspaper</a>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"2\">This is trash.\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Torch.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/b/b2/Torch.png/24px-Torch.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/b/b2/Torch.png/36px-Torch.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/b/b2/Torch.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Torch\" title=\"Torch\">Torch</a>&#160;(3)</span> &#160;<b>90%</b>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Cloth.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/51/Cloth.png/24px-Cloth.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/51/Cloth.png/36px-Cloth.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/5/51/Cloth.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Cloth\" title=\"Cloth\">Cloth</a>&#160;(1)</span> &#160;<b>10%</b>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:Broken_CD.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Broken CD.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/79/Broken_CD.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></div></div>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Broken_CD\" title=\"Broken CD\">Broken CD</a>\n</td>\n<td>It's a JojaNet 2.0 trial CD. They must've made a billion of these things.\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Refined Quartz.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/98/Refined_Quartz.png/24px-Refined_Quartz.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/98/Refined_Quartz.png/36px-Refined_Quartz.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/98/Refined_Quartz.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Refined_Quartz\" title=\"Refined Quartz\">Refined Quartz</a>&#160;(1)</span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:Broken_Glasses.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Broken Glasses.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b5/Broken_Glasses.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></div></div>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Broken_Glasses\" title=\"Broken Glasses\">Broken Glasses</a>\n</td>\n<td>It looks like someone lost their glasses. They're busted.\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Refined Quartz.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/98/Refined_Quartz.png/24px-Refined_Quartz.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/98/Refined_Quartz.png/36px-Refined_Quartz.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/98/Refined_Quartz.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Refined_Quartz\" title=\"Refined Quartz\">Refined Quartz</a>&#160;(1)</span>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Recycling_Machine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-processtime-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-processtime_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">See <samp>Object::performObjectDropInAction</samp> in the game code.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"3\">Equipment\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Crafting#Artisan_Equipment\" title=\"Crafting\">Artisan</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Bee_House\" title=\"Bee House\">Bee House</a> • <a href=\"/Cask\" title=\"Cask\">Cask</a> • <a href=\"/Cheese_Press\" title=\"Cheese Press\">Cheese Press</a> • <a href=\"/Dehydrator\" title=\"Dehydrator\">Dehydrator</a> • <a href=\"/Fish_Smoker\" title=\"Fish Smoker\">Fish Smoker</a> • <a href=\"/Keg\" title=\"Keg\">Keg</a> • <a href=\"/Loom\" title=\"Loom\">Loom</a> • <a href=\"/Mayonnaise_Machine\" title=\"Mayonnaise Machine\">Mayonnaise Machine</a> • <a href=\"/Oil_Maker\" title=\"Oil Maker\">Oil Maker</a> • <a href=\"/Preserves_Jar\" title=\"Preserves Jar\">Preserves Jar</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Crafting#Refining_Equipment\" title=\"Crafting\">Refining</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Bait_Maker\" title=\"Bait Maker\">Bait Maker</a> •  <a href=\"/Bone_Mill\" title=\"Bone Mill\">Bone Mill</a> • <a href=\"/Charcoal_Kiln\" title=\"Charcoal Kiln\">Charcoal Kiln</a> • <a href=\"/Crystalarium\" title=\"Crystalarium\">Crystalarium</a> • <a href=\"/Deluxe_Worm_Bin\" title=\"Deluxe Worm Bin