      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng         = Recycling Machine\n|source      = [[Crafting]]\n|recipe      = {{Name|Fishing Skill Icon|link=Fishing|Level 4}}\n|ingredients = {{Name|Wood|25}}{{Name|Stone|25}}{{Name|Iron Bar|1}}\n|sellprice   = Cannot be sold\n}}\nThe '''Recycling Machine''' is a [[Crafting|crafted]] item that is used to turn [[trash]] (aside from the [[Joja Cola]] and [[Rotten Plant]]) into useful items. It takes {{duration|60m (1h)|class=inline}} to process items.<ref name=\"processtime\"/> The recipe is earned at [[Skills#Fishing|Fishing level 4]].\n\nOne Recycling Machine is the reward for completing the {{Bundle|Field Research||y}}.\n\n==Recycling==\n<section begin=\"trash\" />\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable roundedborder\"\n!Image\n!Name\n!Description\n!Produced from Recycling\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\" | [[File:Trash (item).png|center]]\n|rowspan=\"3\" | [[Trash (item)|Trash]]\n|rowspan=\"3\" | {{Description|Trash}}\n|{{Name|Stone|1-3|class=inline}} &nbsp;'''49%'''\n|-\n|{{Name|Coal|1-3|class=inline}} &nbsp;'''30%'''\n|-\n|class=\"no-wrap\"|{{Name|Iron Ore|1-3|class=inline}} &nbsp;'''21%'''\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\" |[[File:Driftwood.png|center]]\n|rowspan=\"2\" |[[Driftwood]]\n|rowspan=\"2\" |{{Description|Driftwood}}\n|{{Name|Wood|1-3|class=inline}} &nbsp;'''75%'''\n|-\n|{{Name|Coal|1-3|class=inline}} &nbsp;'''25%'''\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\" |[[File:Soggy Newspaper.png|center]]\n|rowspan=\"2\" |[[Soggy Newspaper]]\n|rowspan=\"2\" |{{Description|Soggy Newspaper}}\n|{{Name|Torch|3|class=inline}} &nbsp;'''90%'''\n|-\n|{{Name|Cloth|1|class=inline}} &nbsp;'''10%'''\n|-\n|[[File:Broken CD.png|center]]\n|[[Broken CD]]\n|{{Description|Broken CD}}\n|{{Name|Refined Quartz|1}}\n|-\n|[[File:Broken Glasses.png|center]]\n|[[Broken Glasses]]\n|{{Description|Broken Glasses}}\n|{{Name|Refined Quartz|1}}\n|}<section end=\"trash\" />\n\n==References==\n<references>\n  <ref name=\"processtime\">See <samp>Object::performObjectDropInAction</samp> in the game code.</ref>\n</references>\n\n{{NavboxEquipment}}\n\n[[Category:Craftable items]]\n\n[[de:Recycle-Maschine]]\n[[es:Máquina recicladora]]\n[[fr:Machine de recyclage]]\n[[it:Riciclatore]]\n[[ja:リサイクルマシン]]\n[[ko:재활용 기계]]\n[[hu:Újrahasznosító gép]]\n[[pt:Máquina de reciclagem]]\n[[ru:Утилизационная машина]]\n[[tr:Geri Dönüşüm Makinesi]]\n[[zh:回收机]]"
